  "title": "🦅 Sales Role – Build Skills, Not Just a Resume 💼✨",
  "description": "<p>🌟 <strong>Looking for Fresh Grads & Post-NS Candidates!</strong><br /><strong>🕒</strong> Full-time<br /><strong>💼</strong> New Skills. New Opportunities. Real Growth.</p><p>No experience needed — just the drive to learn and grow.</p><p>Step into a front-facing opportunity where you connect with business owners, build confidence, and gain real-world exposure that actually prepares you for your next career move.</p><p>🔥 <strong>What You’ll Be Exposed To</strong></p><p>• Engage with business owners from different industries<br />• Build real relationships and learn how businesses operate<br />• Work alongside leaders with different styles and learn from their experiences<br />• Share ideas, give input, and grow through hands-on experience</p><p>⭐ <strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></p><p>• Strong communication and people skills you can use anywhere<br />• Confidence in professional and real-world settings<br />• Exposure that helps you understand different leadership styles<br />• Meaningful experience that sets your resume apart</p><p>✔️ <strong>Who This Is For</strong></p><p>• Fresh grads or post-NS individuals<br />• Open-minded, friendly communicators<br />• Motivated learners who enjoy growth and challenge<br />• Those looking for more than just “a job”</p><p>🎯 <strong>Take the First Step</strong><br />If you’re looking for an opportunity to grow, learn, and build real-life skills — this could be for you.</p>",
